rows.label: tlk70000010_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I think everyone did really great in the
defense of the city. But I don't know
how much my opinion really counts.

rows.label: tlk70000010_02_msg0002
rows.name:
What I do know is, that I don't know
what would have happened if you guys
weren't here.

rows.label: tlk70000010_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Course, I have to stay here, but I heard 
on the grapevine that Onyx's squad
helped to fix the place up afterwards.

rows.label: tlk70000010_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I mean, it was by order of the King. But
I still think it's a pretty nice thing of
them to do.

rows.label: tlk70000010_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Usually they just stand about around
the palace, the big meatheads.

rows.label: tlk70000010_02_msg0006
rows.name:
Say, I wonder how Chalcy's getting on.
I hear he's doing well, but I'm trying to
be a bit more hands-off as a bro now.
